# NE Plains WeatherScope

HRRR & NAM weather model viewer for Nebraska and surrounding states.

## Deploy to Vercel

1. Upload all files to GitHub maintaining this folder structure:
   - vercel.json  (at root)
   - api/tiles.js
   - api/meta.js
   - public/index.html

2. Connect repo to Vercel → Deploy

## Data Sources
- NOAA HRRR model via Iowa State IEM tile service
- NEXRAD live radar via Iowa State IEM
- NWS active warnings via Iowa State IEM
- Base maps: CartoDB
